OL,3,CEmergency services respond to reports
OL,4,Cof medical emergency on Aberavon beach
OL,6,FEmergency services are in attendance
OL,7,Fat Aberavon beach in response to
OL,8,Freports of a serious medical incident.
OL,10,FThe nature of the incident is not yet
OL,11,Fclear.
OL,13,FA Welsh Ambulance Service spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "We were called today at
OL,15,Fapproximately 4:07pm, to reports of a
OL,16,Fmedical emergency on Aberavon beach.
