OL,3,CEmergency services respond to reports
OL,4,Cof medical emergency on Aberavon beach
OL,6,F"We sent two Cymru High Acuity
OL,7,FResponse Units, one emergency
OL,8,Fambulance, a hazardous area response
OL,9,Fteam and an operations manager to the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,F"Advanced critical care support was
OL,13,Fdelivered by the Emergency Medical
OL,14,FRetrieval and Transfer Service in a
OL,15,FWales Air Ambulance charity
OL,16,Fhelicopter."
OL,18,FPort Talbot Coastguard Rescue Team, a
OL,19,FRNLI lifeboat from Port Talbot and
OL,20,FSouth Wales Police have also been
OL,21,Fcalled.
